verses.verse: A <S%H7892>Song<s%> of <S%H4609>degrees<s%> of <S%H1732>David.<s%> <S%H3068>Lord,<s%> my <S%H3820>heart<s%> is not <S%H1361>haughty,<s%> <S%H3808>nor<s%> my <S%H5869>eyes<s%> <S%H7311>lofty:<s%> <S%H3808>neither<s%> do I <S%H1980>exercise<s%> myself in <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H1419>matters,<s%> or in things too <S%H6381>high<s%> for me.

<S%H518>Surely<s%> <S%H3808><s%> I have <S%H7737>behaved<s%> and <S%H1826>quieted<s%> <S%H5315>myself,<s%> as a child that is <S%H1580>weaned<s%> of his <S%H517>mother:<s%> my <S%H5315>soul<s%> is even as a <S%H1580>weaned<s%> child.
